Some comments from a customer about this:

{quote}
I can see that with having the ‘file lists’ and the ‘edit in office’ feature we are getting close to not needing a share drive, but to go from a blank document to into a file list you have to
* Create the document
* Save it ‘somewhere’ on  the file system and/or email it to someone
